f embarrassment and damage to all the Western spooks who claimed Russia totally has red lines on being attacked on their territory for last two years... all were proven clearly being clueless with Kursk offensive. So they really needed to take down the one service they haven't backdoored yet that Ukraine could use to get around the dragnet surveillance to avoid such future embarrassments.</p></div>
